{"tid":1574582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今年fg既你，除左搵工仲有一樣更有意義既事要做","createTime":"2019-09-16T13:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T16:13:10.000Z","uid":172295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9ae02ffba2f98915dacdfa255fa59d424c728bcb","tid":1574582,"uid":172295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:12:06.000Z","msg":"就係登記做陪審團<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論你係8大畢業定係top-up畢業又好，<br />\n一定要盡快係10月前寄信，<br />\n點解係10月？<br />\n<br />\n高等法院司法常務官每兩年編製一份陪審員臨時名單，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">該名單於十月或以前擬定，然後在翌年二月或以前確認。</span></strong></span>司法常務官亦可隨時增補該份名單。臨時名單或增補名單一經備妥，司法常務官會在憲報及報章刊登公告，說明該名單已可供查閱。<br />\n<br />\n至於點登記？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eb1pQAZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEb1pQAZ.jpg&h=d47c7ff5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要郵寄，email係唔會受理</span></span></strong><br />\n1) ROP18既Link: <a href=\"http://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/forms/forms/rop18.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fforms%2Fforms%2Frop18.html&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=0ac52df1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/forms/forms/rop18.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2) 信用中文/英文寫自己願意及有能力成為陪審團就可以<br />\n<br />\n3)今年畢業未有畢業證書？<br />\n郵寄左official transcript既副本作學歷證明<br />\n<br />\n另外，2825-3356先可以打去查詢自己係咪已經係陪審團名單。<br />\n相中既2825-4668係唔可以打去查詢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VdPKQBs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVdPKQBs.jpg&h=09421018&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係7月中郵寄去，<br />\n最近收到回信，<br />\n希望今年fg個個都盡快入pool<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces